CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 24, 1956, pg. A22, reads: "Thanksgiving Goodies - Members of the Business and Professional Women's Club of Pittsburgh gave a savory, roasted Thanksgiving turkey and other food to guest at their fall festival at the YWCA. Left to right: Mrs. Marion Bryant, president; Mrs. Jeanne S. Scott, second vice president; Mrs. Lenore Rainey, chairman; Mrs. Elayne Jones, Mrs. Novella Brown, Mrs. Juanita Bands and Mrs. Vera Winslow. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of Business and Professional Women's Club of Pittsburgh from left: Marion Bryant, Jeanne S. Scott, Lenore Rainey, Elayne Jones, Novella Brown, Juanita Bands, and Vera Winslow, posed behind table with turkey at YWCA
